openapi: 3.1.0

info:
  title: Some service
  version: 0.1.0

components:
  schemas:
    item:
      type: object
      additionalProperties:
        type: object
        properties:
          code:
            type: integer
          text:
            type: string
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        title:
          type: string

paths:
  /items:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Get items
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/item'
